data.description: This 5-bedroom, 4 -bathroom home is ideally situated in close proximity to the hospital and beautiful Downtown Jackson. With a perfect blend of historical charm and modern updates, this house offers a unique and captivating living experience. With more than 3600 sqft  this home offers tons of charm and character. From its elegant architectural details to the thoughtfully designed interior spaces, this home showcases the best of both worlds. 2 kitchens ,5 bedrooms and so much more!
